="t m0 x9 h4 yed ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">关系，<span class="_ _3"></span>其实并不是这样。<span class="_ _3"></span>唐密的消失，<span class="_ _3"></span>主要是因为他们宗派</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yee ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">的后学者，<span class="_ _3"></span>没有很好地继承和弘扬这个法脉。<span class="_ _3"></span>这样一来，<span class="_ _3"></span>任</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yef ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">何一种文化最后都会失传的。 </div><div class="t m0 x22 h4 y201 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">但是，<span class="_ _3"></span>藏密的闻思体系、<span class="_ _7"></span>实修体系、<span class="_ _3"></span>传承体系，<span class="_ _7"></span>可以说</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y20f ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">非常完善。<span class="_ _3"></span>正因为如此，<span class="_ _3"></span>藏密弘扬于世这么长时间，<span class="_ _3"></span>不仅跟</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yf2 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">其他文化没有冲突，<span class="_ _3"></span>而且有日益广弘的趋势。<span class="_ _3"></span>这方面，<span class="_ _3"></span>不仅</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
